        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Description:\r\n------------\r\nWhen I try to call action view helper and this action throws exception, exception is not catched by ErrorHandler plugin (and don't goes to my ErrorController).\r\n\r\nReproduce code:\r\n---------------\r\n\r\nlayouts\/scripts\/layout.phtml\r\n<?php echo $this->doctype() ?>\r\n<html xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xhtml\">\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text\/html; charset=utf-8\" \/>\r\n<title>test<\/title>\r\n<\/head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<?php\r\n$this->action('throw', 'index');\r\n?>\r\n\r\n<?php echo $this->layout()->content ?>\r\n\r\n<\/body>\r\n<\/html>\r\n\r\ncontrollers\/IndexController.php\r\nclass IndexController extends Zend_Controller_Action\r\n{\r\n\r\n    public function indexAction()\r\n    {\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    public function throwAction()\r\n    {\r\n       throw new Zend_Controller_Action_Exception('test', 500);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nExpected result:\r\n---------------\r\n\r\nException catched by standart ErrorHandler plugin.\r\n\r\nActual result:\r\n--------------\r\nZend_Controller_Action_Exception: test in \/home\/*****\/applications\/admin\/controllers\/IndexController.php on line 18\r\nCall Stack\r\n#\tTime\tMemory\tFunction\tLocation\r\n1\t0.0002\t317624\t{main}( )\t..\/index.php:0\r\n2\t0.0007\t331576\trequire_once( '\/home\/*****\/public\/start.php' )\t..\/index.php:7\r\n3\t0.2006\t5813536\tZend_Application->run( )\t..\/start.php:59\r\n4\t0.2006\t5813536\tZend_Application_Bootstrap_Bootstrap->run( )\t..\/Application.php:366\r\n5\t0.2008\t5813592\tZend_Controller_Front->dispatch( )\t..\/Bootstrap.php:97"
        },
